    <item>
      <title>韩国启动路演，向石油巨头推介大型海上油气资源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/korea-launches-roadshow-to-pitch-big-offshore-find-to-oil-majors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在全球石油巨头对一处海上油田表现出兴趣之后，韩国目前正在举办投资者路演，这在亚洲国家引发了兴奋和怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/korea-launches-roadshow-to-pitch-big-offshore-find-to-oil-majors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 08:17:46 GMT</pubDate>
