    <item>
      <title>印度限制债券持有，阻止全球基金进入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/india-will-shield-some-newly-issued-debt-from-foreign-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度对部分新发行债券的外资持股比例实施了管制，这一出人意料的举措凸显出印度官员对将印度债券纳入全球关键指数后引发的数十亿美元热钱流入感到不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/india-will-shield-some-newly-issued-debt-from-foreign-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 01:31:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>必和必拓以 30 亿美元收购 Filo 南美铜矿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/bhp-group-and-canada-s-lundin-mining-buy-copper-miner-filo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团有限公司 (BHP Group Ltd.) 刚刚遭到英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc) 的拒绝，便出手收购了 Filo Corp.，并与 Lundin Mining Corp. 联手以 30 亿美元的价格获得了南美两个铜矿项目的权利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/bhp-group-and-canada-s-lundin-mining-buy-copper-miner-filo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 00:02:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
